Paul Bartel https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Bartel 0 Paul Bartel (August 6, 1938 – May 13, 2000) was an American actor, writer and director. Bartel was perhaps most known for his 1982 hit black comedy Eating Raoul, which he wrote, starred in and directed.
